            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "When developing/contributing to plugins, I often (have to) switch between upstream and my local checkout for testing WIP changes on the feature branch, or quick A/B testing between the branch and `main`. Being able to simply point the plugin manager to the checkout temporarily reduces _a lot_ of friction for this.",
